short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Organise your all tasks at a single place.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "My ToDo List" is a chrome extension that allows you to write and organise your tasks or works that you want to do or planning to do in a single place. If you are a busy person and have a lot of tasks/works to do online and you don't want to forget them, install "My ToDo List" in your browser. It will remember and manage all your tasks.
